          <p style="font-weight: bold">INSPIRATION</p>
          <p>Exploring aspects surrounding men, Helios searches for iconic imagery with strong connections to their stories.</p>
          <p style="font-weight: bold">SKETCHING</p>
          <p>Based on the main symbol, the design team begins sketching the first images on paper. Stylized lines must convey the spirit of the idea while also showing Helios' distinctive signature.</p>
          <p style="font-weight: bold">3D MODELING</p>
          <p>From hand-drawn sketches, the digital design team creates 3D models with the help of graphic software. This model is then 3D printed with liquid wax material, specifically serving the metal casting field. The finished wax mold is the original template of the creation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card_item">
        <div class="about-card_item_img">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0644/2958/8701/files/mg_8070_optimized.webp?v=1709267770" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-card_item_content">
          <p style="font-weight: bold">CLOSED SILVER WORKSHOP</p>
          <p>At the closed silver workshop, Helios craftsmen carry out the molding process from the wax tree. Using premium S925 silver, heated until molten then poured into the mold to create the silver tree, each branch corresponding to a product. Once the silver tree is obtained, each branch is separated and goes through grinding - polishing - oxidizing processes.</p>
          <p>The entire process is carefully and meticulously performed by skilled craftsmen. Therefore, each product is unique, and there can never be a second identical piece.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
